==位置==
这个站位于[[北京市|北京市]][[房山区|房山区]][[良乡东路|良乡东路]]（东西向）与[[长于大街|长于大街]]（南北向）交汇处以南，呈南北走向。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bjghw.gov.cn/web/static/articles/catalog_14300/article_ff808081271d5bde01278a0a8f0901ce/ff808081271d5bde01278a0a8f0901ce.html|title=轨道交通房山线规划方案公告|publisher=[[北京市规划委员会|北京市规划委员会]]|date=2010-03-23|accessdate=2010-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100728091831/http://www.bjghw.gov.cn/web/static/articles/catalog_14300/article_ff808081271d5bde01278a0a8f0901ce/ff808081271d5bde01278a0a8f0901ce.html|archive-date=2010-07-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

